examples.en: He would brook no interruptions from subordinates.
I still go on working, but with terrible interruptions.
Her poor pestered father had to endure her constant interruptions.
The continual interruptions by the student were annoying the teacher.
Please go ahead with your story, there won't be any more interruptions.
Constant interruptions discomfited her in her attempt to finish the speech, and she finally gave up.
